channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.description: *before*: This Service is to help Client deploy IBM Power technologies based on a jointly developed plan and targeted use cases, *after*: IBM will help implement a backup and restore solution for IBM Power Virtual Server (PowerVS) using IBM Storage Protect for Cloud. IBM will assist with a rapid deployment of the IBM Storage Protect environment including associated storage, as well as the connectivity of IBM Storage Protect agents on PowerVS to the IBM Storage Protect server for one IBM Storage Protect server environment and up to four IBM Storage Protect clients.
